WEBVTT

00:00.016 --> 00:01.548
Previously on <i>This Is Us</i>...

00:01.554 --> 00:02.976
The drinking has to stop.

00:02.982 --> 00:06.377
We have to rein it in baby because I
won't have it in my house.

00:06.383 --> 00:07.617
Although when we were together

00:07.618 --> 00:08.918
she said she never
wanted to get married.

00:08.966 --> 00:09.966
Hey, meet Gus.

00:09.992 --> 00:11.210
<i>Yeah, it was very brief.</i>

00:11.216 --> 00:13.476
<i>It was another life. Probably
why she didn't tell you.</i>

00:13.482 --> 00:15.096
You think that I didn't deserve to know

00:15.130 --> 00:16.964
<i>that you had history with him?</i>

00:16.999 --> 00:19.976
You know, you never really
talk about your dad's death.

00:19.992 --> 00:24.095
It's been, um, just blocked
for a really long time.

00:24.539 --> 00:26.775
WILLIAM: <i>Roll all your
windows down, Randall.</i>

00:26.781 --> 00:28.242
<i>Crank up the music.</i>

00:28.248 --> 00:30.570
<i>Let someone else make your bed.</i>

00:34.164 --> 00:35.306
(gasps for air softly)

00:36.742 --> 00:37.742
Mm.

00:38.534 --> 00:40.007
(gentle guitar strumming)

